{"id":232635160,"title":"香氛沐浴乳開箱","content":"冬天冷阿，\n雖然衣服穿得多還是要洗香香，\n夏天洗的涼感我都把它咻的收起來了，\n買了幾款沐浴乳，來實測一下，選手出場!!\n1號選手 台灣花香 ~   \nhttps://i.imgur.com/oepmwQH.jpg\n2號選手 德國Frosch ~  \nhttps://i.imgur.com/gG0g1gG.jpg\n3號選手 日本biore !  \nhttps://i.imgur.com/yZ6IthA.jpg\n\n1號 活力清爽 辣木精華\n泡沫量 ★★★★★\n味道★★★\n洗完觸感 ★★★★\n\n2號 石榴   \n泡沫量 ★★★★\n味道★★★★\n洗完觸感 ★★★★★\n\n3號 千葉玫瑰  \n泡沫量 ★★★\n味道★★★★\n洗完觸感 ★★★\n\n心得:\n1號保水感還不錯，但他像乳液的質感我不太喜歡，剛洗完微黏，香味我覺得濃郁感比較重味道部分海洋香基底OK，日常用中規中矩。\n\n2號的成分天然，PH值接近肌膚，所以洗起來蠻舒服的，泡沫量中等，是優點或缺點見仁見智，剛起泡的時候味道比較強，出浴後肌膚水感有淡淡的酸甜滋味，挺俏皮的很適合拿來征服男友\n\n3號一打開的前味是還蠻不錯的，小可惜是起泡真的有點困難，洗完滑順玫瑰的香我也很喜歡，味道偏成熟","excerpt":"冬天冷阿，雖然衣服穿得多還是要洗香香，夏天洗的涼感我都把它咻的收起來了，買了幾款沐浴乳，來實測一下，選手出場！！，1號選手 台灣花香 ~，2號選手 德國Frosch ~，3號選手 日本biore ！，","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"1a14ba93-3989-47e5-aedc-a3918963100e","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-06T05:03:33.201Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-06T12:10:44.117Z","commentCount":13,"likeCount":21,"tags":[],"topics":["沐浴乳","香氛","開箱"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"香氛","forumAlias":"fragrance","school":"亞洲大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":21}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/oepmwQH.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/gG0g1gG.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/yZ6IthA.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"bac77865-0d9d-40aa-9b33-2c3dee4c7468","url":"https://i.imgur.com/oepmwQHl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/oepmwQHl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/oepmwQHl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-06T05:03:33.201Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-06T12:10:44.117Z"},{"id":"bac77865-0d9d-40aa-9b33-2c3dee4c7468","url":"https://i.imgur.com/oepmwQH.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://